                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "In his new book, the writer tries to <w>denounce</w> the social inequality in society."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Met deze felle toespraak wilde de politicus het wanbeleid van de regering <w>aanklagen</w>.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "With this fierce speech, the politician wanted to <w>denounce</w> the government's mismanagement."
